        {
            "id": 5930071,
            "title": "《大手成交》盈富基金一手約136萬股自動交叉盤,涉2755萬",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社9日專訊》盈富基金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02800:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02800\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02800-HK</a>)於10:19am錄得1手136.25萬股自動交叉盤,每股造20.22元,較上日收市價低0.5%,涉資2755萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　盈富基金現價跌0.7%,報20.18元;成交2.01億股,成交金額40.03億元,主動買沽比率58:42,資金淨主動買入5.82億元。(rw)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
